title: Streaming some Riot Ranked 5s =)

replies.body: Gehirn still playing sej i see
It started out like "Imma play the least popular champion", then it became "Oh we need tank, AP, peel, and aoe cc - guess you're playing Sej" and now I'm an accidental Sejuani main.

We had a group of 5 people online the whole time you were streaming, sitting in a lobby (and then, obviously, queuing up whenever you did) trying to snipe you.
But it never happened :(
RIP haha your team must be tooo good for ours =P

Great stream.
Needs less Benji playing jungle though :P
